<span id="freeTextContainer7112210685413116952"><a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/261689.The_Grand_Sophy' title='The Grand Sophy by Georgette Heyer' rel='nofollow noopener'>The Grand Sophy</a>, my first <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/18067.Georgette_Heyer' title='Georgette Heyer' rel='nofollow noopener'>Georgette Heyer</a>, is a very entertaining book about a complete hoyden who turns people&apos;s lives upside down. The vivacious, unconventional and head-strong Sophy is a delightful heroine. She comes to stay at her aunt when her diplomatic father has to sail away to Brazil, of all places. She soons detects many problems that the family is struggling with, and decides to intervene. For their own good, of course. <br/><br/><i>The Grand Sophy</i> is the perfect read when you need a lull from den</span>
  <span id="freeText7112210685413116952" style="display:none"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/261689.The_Grand_Sophy" title="The Grand Sophy by Georgette Heyer" rel="nofollow noopener">The Grand Sophy</a>, my first <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/18067.Georgette_Heyer" title="Georgette Heyer" rel="nofollow noopener">Georgette Heyer</a>, is a very entertaining book about a complete hoyden who turns people's lives upside down. The vivacious, unconventional and head-strong Sophy is a delightful heroine. She comes to stay at her aunt when her diplomatic father has to sail away to Brazil, of all places. She soons detects many problems that the family is struggling with, and decides to intervene. For their own good, of course. <br /><br /><i>The Grand Sophy</i> is the perfect read when you need a lull from denser, darker ones. It is fast-paced, clever and funny. <br /><br />Perfect brain-candy. Enjoy!</span>
